CatDescriptText: Cutline of images published in the Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 24, 1956, pg. A26 reads: "Teen Queen Contest Going Great - With the 1956 Hill Top Teen Queen contest getting into its stride..."
TitMainTitle: Two frames: Portrait of Beverly Howze wearing light colored sweater, shirt with rounded collar, and hoop earrings, posed for Hill City Teen Queen contest; Portrait of Lorraine Tate wearing a light colored blouse with flower brooch pinned at collar, posed for Hill City Teen Queen contest
